https://discord.gg/sSkta8C

originally a pretty active 61A server, but since most of us are going to start taking a lot more ee and cs courses, we thought we might as well turn this into a general (ee)cs server! 

I'll post this again when next semester starts, but I thought it might be helpful during deadweek as people are preparing for finals. Right now it's only lower-div stuff but if you're taking upper divs still join because we'll definitely add more upper div support if enough people are here for it!
